N2  - The article reports on the use of the Delphi method in long-range technological forecasting. The author's opinions regarding the recruitment of professionals for Delphi experimentation are presented. He suggests that variances in professionals' degrees of expertise, as well as their opinions, could affect the forecasting results. Short-range forecasting is also discussed.
